Add the following to .bashrc (metafont is expected to segfault when these are not set):
  export SCREEN_WIDTH=$(xrandr|grep current|cut -d, -f2|cut -d' ' -f3)
  export SCREEN_DEPTH=$(xrandr|grep current|cut -d, -f2|cut -d' ' -f5)

It is assumed that this repo is in /home/user.

Use the companion repo http://github.com/igor-liferenko/mf-wayland
